{"tid":1992073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：決定是否延長限聚令時 不會考慮示威集會情況","createTime":"2020-04-28T02:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T03:53:06.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3cf77a49c1d546bef46a6c08362299161f2335","tid":1992073,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"警方日前在太古城處理反修例示威時，警告在場的人涉嫌違反「限聚令」，最終未有票控。行政長官林鄭月娥表示，檢控與否要視乎法律、證據和檢控守則，指相關法例其中一個元素是「有否共同目的」，如果市民各自上班等巴士，或者等升降機，並沒有共同目的，就不會違反法例；如果一家六口拜山，雖然有共同目的，但也有豁免。她強調相關法例已經平衡市民日常生活，以及控制疫情的需要。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，政府決定是否延長限聚令時，只是考慮公共衛生、經濟影響及市民承受能力，不會考慮示威集會情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283882&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283882%26csid%3D261_341&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=23017b59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283882&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"696028058465a7c47058343b755caf9a0150b3de","tid":1992073,"uid":41873,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好撚玩我啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4acc65493d3bed8c6ec756ed4e0fb7f5ba73c216","tid":1992073,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"即係會"},{"pid":"187c1370592b58444e3778ee8871cc573b1184ec","tid":1992073,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"佢原句：每年有萬幾個遊行示威 冇可能考慮"},{"pid":"c4a412c4a81b40c9267c8271fdd7cf081812f640","tid":1992073,"uid":187957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"拜山有得EXEMPT咩?"},{"pid":"8fc9458b442673cb9b21a3dc23d1eb7f4f41abc5","tid":1992073,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2